post_list.message: Hello! I am the Planner, and I can help you by coordinating with the CodeInterpreter to complete tasks that involve generating and running Python code. You can tell me what you need, and I will create a step-by-step plan to accomplish it. If the task requires coding, I will instruct the CodeInterpreter to write and execute the necessary Python code. How can I assist you today?
